{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-29","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 29","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kod numerisane liste (<code>ol</code>) je isti kao nenumerisana lista, ali stavke u numerisanoj listi dobijaju brojeve kada se prikazuju.</p>\n<p>Ispod elementa <code>h3</code>, dodajte listu sa ovim tri stavke liste:</p>\n<p><code>flea treatment</code>\n<code>thunder</code>\n<code>other cats</code></p>\n</section>","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804d2","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-29"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        \n      </section>\n    </main>\n\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[23,25],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoj element <code>ol</code> treba da ima oznaku za aktivaciju. Oznake za aktivaciju imaju ovu sintaksu: <code>&#x3C;elementName></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.exists(document.querySelector('ol'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>ol</code> treba da ima zatvarajući tag. Zatvarajući tagovi su <code>/</code> odmah nakon karaktera <code>&#x3C;</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<\\/ol>/);"},{"text":"<p>Element za <code>ol</code> bi trebalo da bude iznad zatvarajuće oznake drugog elementa <code>section</code>. Pogrešno ste ga postavili po redosledu.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelectorAll('main > section')[1]?.lastElementChild.nodeName, 'OL');"},{"text":"<p>Tri elementa od <code>li</code> treba da budu postavljeni unutar elementa <code>ol</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(\n  [...document.querySelectorAll('li')].filter(\n    (item) => item.parentNode.nodeName === 'OL'\n  ), 3\n);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš tri elementa sa <code>li</code> koji sadrže tekst <code>flea treatment</code>, <code>thunder</code> i <code>other cats</code> u bilo kom redosledu.</p>","testString":"assert.deepStrictEqual(\n  [...document.querySelectorAll('li')]\n    .filter((item) => item.parentNode.nodeName === 'OL')\n    .map((item) => item.innerText?.trim().replace(/\\s+/g, ' ').toLowerCase())\n    .sort((a, b) => a.localeCompare(b)),\n  ['flea treatment', 'other cats', 'thunder']\n);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da ima samo jedan element <code>ol</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf([...document.querySelectorAll('ol')], 1);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-29","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","chapter":"html","module":"basic-html","block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-30","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-28","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804d2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-29"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}